Telkom has launched the Huawei P20 and P20 Lite on its network. The company said the new smartphones are available on Telkom FreeMe contracts from today. “The P20 Pro will be available from 13 April 2018,” added Telkom. The devices are available on FreeMe 1GB, 2GB, 5GB, 10GB, 20GB, and Unlimited, for both new and existing Telkom subscribers. Telkom said the starting contract prices for the Huawei P20 range are: